title: Valhalla 1-15 (complete)
description:
Valhalla is the most famous Danish comic, a great comic for all ages, about the nordic gods.
After 8 years I FINALLY finished the project, with the help of JJ, Alice, and Chevalley doing retexting.

So now you can finally grab the FULL Valhalla collection. Enjoy this classic danish comic.


Apparently Piratebay messes up if the description is too long, so my nice info about all 15 comics, links to preview pics, are all gone. But if you know Valhalla, you know what you get, and if not, get it, and read it complete in english for the first time :)
